query:
INSERT INTO weekly_snapshots (userId, weekStart, weekEnd, totalGross, daysWorked, createdAt)
SELECT 
  30001 as userId,
  '2025-10-27' as weekStart,
  '2025-11-03' as weekEnd,
  SUM(amount) as totalGross,
  COUNT(DISTINCT date) as daysWorked,
  NOW() as createdAt
FROM earnings
WHERE userId = 30001 
  AND date >= '2025-10-27' 
  AND date < '2025-11-03';
